nodes.text: "Rachet" Gramzee was a male Ugnaught who lived during the waning years of the Galactic Republic. "Rachet" might have been his nickname. The Corporate Alliance placed a bounty on his head for stealing a chemical process used in the production of death sticks. The bounty was claimed by bounty hunter Jango Fett, who caught him. It's possible that he was an accomplice to Lokk Gimble, who was wanted for the same crime.
